Class OrderRepository<T extends Order>

java.lang.Object
hr.java.restaurant.repository.AbstractRepository<T>
hr.java.restaurant.repository.OrderRepository<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the order, extending the Order class.
public class OrderRepository<T extends Order> extends AbstractRepository<T>
Repository for managing orders in the restaurant system. Provides functionality for reading orders from a file, saving orders to a file, and retrieving orders based on their ID.
